title: New Creator: Joe Bartolozzi
body:
Name: Joe Bartolozzi

Socials -
https://www.twitch.tv/joe_bartolozzi
https://www.tiktok.com/@joe.bartolozzi?lang=en
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGRryxFxjXbVAtBPE9EbyMg?view_as=subscriber

Info - Joe Bartolozzi is a very well known content creator across Tik Tok, Twitch, and YouTube. With over 9 million total followers across his platforms, Joe has a large reach in the creator space. Known for his funny gameplay, unique opinions on video games, and viral reactions to Tik Tok videos, Joe has a highly engaged audience. 

Use Cases -
Coin distribution - Youtube / Tik Tok / Twitch 
Holding - exclusive content from YouTube, Discord roles and channels, video game tournaments
Transacting - Q&As on stream, requested Tik Tok content, video game tournaments, play with me, 1 on 1 calls  

Grant - $1000

A 'yes' approves Joe Bartolozzi and a $1000 treasury grant
A 'no' denies this prop.
